title.narrative: Telephone Communications Expenses - All Other Telephone Communications NOC. 16/17 WCF: ENET - OpenNet/ClassNet. Telephone Communications Expenses - Telephone Equipment Installation and Service

description.narrative: This covers all other telephone communications costs that are not otherwise classified.. Covers the costs of rental of telephone sets, switchboards, etc., from the organization operating the telephone facilities. Includes on post transmission lines where local custom dictates.
